what_worked: Applied decorrelate, single_pass_aggregation: Eliminated the correlated subquery by precomputing manufacturers with matching items in a CTE, then performed a single join instead of per-row subquery executions.
why_it_worked: Correlated subqueries re-execute per outer row; converting to JOIN eliminates per-row overhead; Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1
